{"tid":947983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國搞人臉識別","createTime":"2018-12-19T16:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T07:15:40.000Z","uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"20e98ad4714498c5340c9db482d8562351f618bd","tid":947983,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/12/19/london-police-face-recognition-technology/life-tech/?fbclid=IwAR3vQyq1ibsDk7Svv9PL_RQZntTB8XjuE8h-uDQGJbF_Ro1_PNPd4t4EaME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F12%2F19%2Flondon-police-face-recognition-technology%2Flife-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3vQyq1ibsDk7Svv9PL_RQZntTB8XjuE8h-uDQGJbF_Ro1_PNPd4t4EaME&d=CplsXHUpDta2qU6L8%2Fp1%2FZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d81cf356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/12/19/london-police-face-recognition-technology/life-tech/?fbclid=IwAR3vQyq1ibsDk7Svv9PL_RQZntTB8XjuE8h-uDQGJbF_Ro1_PNPd4t4EaME</a><br />\n<br />\n脫歐後分分鐘周街搶野 整定差唔多"},{"pid":"bc64f601c9ab8538aaf9800ab22b46d2db46a153","tid":947983,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"倫敦西區及華埠逛街購物<br />\n被警方「掃臉」<br />\n<br />\n倫敦首都警察廳使用最新科技，識別街上每個人。但臉部識別技術（FRT）並非沒有爭議，事實上這已經警方第二次試用這一技術，警方稱，在維持治安和反恐方面，FRT是十分有效的方法。<br />\n現在，倫敦Soho、Piccadilly Circus和Leicester Square一帶已經設有流動的人臉識別裝置，警方還準備了最新科技小冊子，解釋「掃臉」過程，派發給公眾。<br />\n裝置已於12月17、18日試試用，每日運作8小時左右。警察廳發言人表示，希望今次試用後，臉部識別技術的使用「更為廣泛」。<br />\n與以往不同的是，警方將主動「邀請」人們掃臉，並保證若某位市民不願意被掃描，警方不會將其當作可疑人物。<br />\n今年5月，維權團體「Big Brother Watch」通過陽光法案獲取數據，發現警方聲稱的臉部掃描「有98%程度的高吻合度」實為錯誤。「Big Brother Watch」表示，現在警方獲得的吻合度更差了，已經達到100%。組織主席Silkie Carlo表示，警方所推的新科技是極權式的，缺乏合乎民主法律程序的背書。<br />\nFRT技術採用特殊攝像頭，將紅外線投射到人臉上。機器分析被掃描者臉部上採集的三萬個點，構造出人臉3D模型，機器將進一步分析雙眼之間的距離、顴骨高低等特徵。分析結果將與警方數據庫 Police National Database的資料互相比對。<br />\n據稱，FRT技術曾成功判斷人的年齡、性別、情感及其他信息，但面對同一人拍的兩張不同照片時，誤判率極高。尤其是碰上非白種人的案例時，幾乎全錯。<br />\n<br />\n在剛過去的周一、二，在倫敦西區和里斯特廣場逛街的行人，會被警方進行「臉部掃描」。"},{"pid":"a9a41d9220a1fd8ca5e59f3e14953264c61b0f8a","tid":947983,"uid":81424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"同納粹中國搞埋同一樣野嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d4c6f7888f01b359eb92e62c45083e6e5ba879","tid":947983,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a9a41d9220a1fd8ca5e59f3e14953264c61b0f8a","tid":947983,"uid":81424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"同納粹中國搞埋同一樣野嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"英國整可能有另一種睇法"},{"pid":"e531a1facd922bef20eb4ea72f7f92f3bc74682f","tid":947983,"uid":145496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"唔怪得唔肯ban華為，原來要佢技術支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344631121e2beeaa4a7c5f6146e1a08612783ad2","tid":947983,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:22:40.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf04ee8593f72156989655e8a5c227cb4eaa7b5a","tid":947983,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e531a1facd922bef20eb4ea72f7f92f3bc74682f","tid":947983,"uid":145496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"唔怪得唔肯ban華為，原來要佢技術支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"你咁講又似似地<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07b2bbdc4c96ddf8688b038f724d07c64747f12","tid":947983,"uid":10210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T19:08:23.000Z","msg":"英國同支那FD 過打BAND<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caeec598bd903faecaea10add142b0e31c29d0b","tid":947983,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T20: